 spatial temperature fluctuations, as expected during\nhelium reionization, or additional processes that heat a significant volume\nfraction of the low-density IGM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Nov 2016 18:32:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-25"}
