 distance across which dark photons must propagate from their point of\nproduction to be able to affect the star. This work clarifies the bounds from\nSN1987A on the dark-photon parameter space.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Nov 2016 21:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Jan 2017 19:18:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 12 Feb 2018 21:16:22 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 31 May 2019 21:23:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-04"}
