ution is\nunknown, and it does not assume strict proportionality of the neutrino flux to\nthe measured 2LAC $\\gamma$-ray signal for each source. Additionally, we\nconstrain recent models for neutrino emission by blazars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Nov 2016 21:02:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-31"}
