9 patients of a total population of 9,620 patients,\nwhich corresponds to 410 more patients than the most competitive benchmark\nalgorithm (DeepBoost).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 12 Nov 2016 01:53:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-15"}
